---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="OceanicFin - Blue Economy, Marine Finance & Ocean Investment"
  description="Insights on sustainable ocean investment, marine finance, maritime trade, offshore banking, and blue economy opportunities worldwide."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">OceanicFin</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">OceanicFin</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Blue Economy & Marine Finance Hub</h1>
    <p>Your trusted source for ocean investment insights, maritime trade analysis, and sustainable blue economy opportunities.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Sustainable Ocean Investment</h2>
      <p>Blue bonds, ocean-linked funds, and ESG-aligned marine portfolios are reshaping capital markets. Explore how investors are funding ocean conservation while generating returns.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Marine Finance & Shipping</h2>
      <p>Global shipping finance, vessel leasing, and port infrastructure funding. Analysis of freight rates, fleet expansion, and the transition to green maritime logistics.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Maritime Trade Corridors</h2>
      <p>Key shipping routes, trade volume trends, and geopolitical factors shaping global maritime commerce. From the Suez Canal to Arctic passages and Indo-Pacific lanes.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Offshore Banking & Regulation</h2>
      <p>Offshore financial centers, maritime tax frameworks, and regulatory developments. How coastal jurisdictions are balancing competitiveness with transparency.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Ocean Technology & Innovation</h2>
      <p>Aquaculture tech, deep-sea mining ventures, wave energy startups, and marine biotech. The emerging sectors driving the next wave of blue economy growth.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Blue Economy Outlook</h2>
      <p>The global ocean economy is projected to exceed $3 trillion by 2030. Sector forecasts for fisheries, coastal tourism, renewable energy, and marine biotechnology.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>
